Package uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.impl.get

Operations for retrieving elements from a Gaffer graph.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GetAdjacentIds
    A GetAdjacentIds operation will return the vertex at the opposite end of connected edges to a provided seed vertex.
    GetAdjacentIds.Builder  
    GetAllElements
    Extends GetAllElements, but fetches all elements from the graph that are compatible with the provided view.
    GetAllElements.Builder  
    GetElements
    Gets elements from Gaffer based on ElementIds as seeds and returns Elements There are various flags to filter out the elements returned: seedMatching - can either be SeedMatchingType.RELATED or SeedMatchingType.EQUAL.
    GetElements.Builder  
    GetFromEndpoint
    A GetFromEndpoint is an Operation that will fetch data from a provided endpoint.
    GetFromEndpoint.Builder
